e base texas and in june  became an air training officer at the newly established us air force academy then temporarily located at lowry air force base colo general hecker was next assigned to the th tactical fighter squadron th tactical fighter wing at royal air force station wethersfield england flying fs upon returning to the united states in june  general hecker was assigned to the th combat crew training group at luke air force base ariz while at luke he served as flight commander and later as chief of the plans programming and scheduling section th combat crew training group in august  general hecker was assigned to headquarters tactical air command langley air force base va as a staff officer in fighter operations he entered the royal air force command and staff college in december  after graduation he was assigned to the th tactical fighter squadron rd tactical fighter wing bien hoa air base republic of vietnam while there he flew  combat missions in fs in august  general hecker was assigned to headquarters us air force washington dc as chief regular general officer matters office of the deputy chief of staff personnel after graduation from the national war college in  general hecker was assigned to plattsburgh air force base ny as the commander of the th bombardment squadron th bombardment wing flying fbs in april  he became assistant deputy commander for operations of the th bombardment wing and in august  became deputy commander for operations in july  he assumed the responsibilities of deputy commander for maintenance in may  general hecker took command of the th bombardment wing at pease air force base nh and in january  became commander of the th air division also at pease from december  to april  general hecker served as special assistant for mx matters office of the deputy chief of staff research development and acquisition headquarters us air force he assumed his present duties in may  general hecker is a command pilot with more than  flying hours including  combat hours his military decorations and awards include the silver star legion of merit with oak leaf cluster distinguished flying cross bronze star medal meritorious service medal with oak leaf cluster air medal with nine oak leaf clusters air force commendation medal republic of vietnam gallantry cross with palm and republic of vietnam armed forces honor medal st class he also wears the missile badge he was promoted to major general sept   with date of rank july   current as of august  site mapigaf sitesaf executive fleetquestionsfoiacontact ussapr usagovno fear actrssaccessibilityeeolink disclaimerstrategic aprsuicide prevention subscribe to usaf news and information submit guy l hecker jr  former president at stafford burke  hecker inc news home advertising board and executive moves energy health care hedge funds m  a private equity technology you have ¬†  free profiles ¬† left this month ¬†¬† start your free trial ‚û§ hey we noticed youre a relsci pro subscriber would you like to view the page there view on relsci pro ‚û§ email linkedin facebook google tweet reddit permalink guy l hecker jr former president at stafford burke  hecker inc overview in the news relationships paths education career history boards  committees political donations public holdings guy l hecker jr former president at stafford burke  hecker inc overview age  born  notable companies stafford burke  hecker inc board seats  number of relationships this person is connected to  people in the news see more business wire september   x inc appoints vikram verma as chief executive officer relationships see details bryan r martin chief technology officer at x inc vikram verma chief executive officer at x inc ralph f tice former interim chief executive officer at the citadel foundation m russell holliday member board of directors at the citadel foundation john w rosa president at the citadel the military college of south carolina paul c aughtry iii professional at ahg hotels llc stephen l